data.name: TermsOfService
data.value: Thank you for downloading and using our remote control app for your Repetier Server Pro server. Please note that we are not responsable of any demage or failed prints caused by using or misusing our app. We recommend you to never control your printer when you are not in the same room or nearby. This includes, among other things, the control of the printer axis, pausing and resuming prints, remotely control temperatures and so on. It's also commonly recommended to never leave your printer unattended! The use of this app is on your own risk.
